videos.headline: McClendon finds Hurd for the TD
videos.description: Jalan McClendon finds Jalen Hurd for 25 yards for Baylor's first touchdown of the 2018 season.

videos.headline: Baylor WR Jones cashes in TD after turnover
videos.description: Baylor QB Jalan McClendon throws 20-yrd TD to WR Marques Jones.

videos.headline: Abilene Christian McCrary runs for 75-yard TD
videos.description: Abilene Christian Billy McCrary breaks out for 75-yard touchdown run for the Wildcats.

videos.headline: Baylor's Lovett ruining TD adds to big lead
videos.description: Baylor's John Lovett runs in a 31-yard touchdown to extend Baylor's lead before halftime.

videos.headline: Abilene Christian's Cokley makes sliding TD catch
videos.description: Abilene Christian's Chase Cokley brings in a sliding touchdown catch to shrink the Baylor lead.
